difficultyEnabled 
Game: Armed Assault (1.05) 
Description: Checks specific difficulty settings of the current user. Difficulty 
 flag names can be found in the ArmA profile file under class Difficulties 
/xxx/Flags (xxx being regular or veteran).  
Syntax:  
 Boolean = difficultyEnabled flagName 
Parameters: 
flagName: String - difficulty flag name 
Return Value: 
 Boolean